name: Feeling Low, Feeling High
description:
Last week was pretty rough on many levels, mostly on my mental health. So, I did this little animation last night since I couldn't fall asleep. It's nothing special, but it represents how my mind was in the past few days. Having low moments, but also some high moments, trying to not get overwhelmed by everything. All I can do is take one day at a time. 

2160x2160
30fps
software: Procreate
